error_notGoogle: The URL should be https://<subdomain>.blogspot.com, please check again.
error_noProfile: No profile, please add one at least
error_invalidGoogleToken: No or invalid Google token. Please authorize again.
error_profileNotMatch: Blogger profile not match. Which one do you want to use?
command_publishWithDefault: Publish current note with default options
server_googleOAuth2TokenObtained: Google token obtained successfully! You can close this window now.
server_googleOAuth2StateMismatch: Google OAuth2 request and response mismatch.: <%= req %> vs <%= res %>
server_googleOAuth2InvalidResponse: Google authorization response is invalid.: <%= response %>
settings_urlDesc: Full path of installed Blogger, for example, https://example.com/wordpress
settings_apiTypeDesc: Select which API you want to use.
settings_apiTypeXmlRpcDesc: XML-RPC was enabled by default but some sites may disable it because of security problems.
settings_apiTypeRestMiniOrangeDesc: REST API was enabled by default in Blogger 4.7+. These APIs should be authenticated by extra plugin miniOrange which should be installed and enabled in Blogger server.
settings_apiTypeRestApplicationPasswords: REST API Authentication by application passwords
REST API was enabled by default in Blogger 4.7+ while application passwords was introduced in Blogger 5.6+.
settings_showRibbonIconDesc: If enabled, a button which opens publish panel will be added to the Obsidian sidebar.
settings_defaultPostStatusDesc: Post status which will be published to Blogger.
settings_rememberLastSelectedCategoriesD: Remember last selected post categories of this site.
settings_showBloggerEditPageModalDesc: Show open Blogger edit page confirmation when publish successfully
settings_googleOAuth2AuthorizeTokenDesc: Click right button to validate or authorize Google OAuth2 token.
settings_defaultPostCommentDesc: Comment status which will be published to Blogger.
settings_MathJaxOutputTypeTeXDesc: Convert MathJax to TeX directly. Blogger needs install MathJax related plugin, such as simple-mathjax.
settings_MathJaxOutputTypeSVGDesc: Convert MathJax to SVG. Browser render SVG, no plugin needed for Blogger.
settings_enableHtmlDesc: Enable HTML tags in notes. This might cause XSS attack to your Blogger.
settings_replaceMediaLinksDesc: Replace media links to Blogger URLs after uploading.
loginModal_rememberUsernameDesc: If enabled, the Blogger username you typed will be saved in local data. This might be disclosure in synchronize services.
loginModal_rememberPasswordDesc: If enabled, the Blogger password you typed will be saved in local data. This might be disclosure in synchronize services.
publishModal_wrongMatterDataForPage: There are tags or categories in matter-data which are not allowed for page. Are you sure to delete these data?
publishedModal_confirmEditInWP: Do you want to open Blogger edit page in browser?
profilesChooserModal_pickOne: Click to pick one profile to publish.
profileNotMatch_useNew: Create a new post using "<%= profileName %>"
